de.fhg.iml.vlog.xftour.model
Class XFNode

java.lang.Object
  de.fhg.iml.vlog.xftour.model.XFNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class XFNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Nodes are the basic structure of this optimization model. The tour representation relies on nodes. Depots and customers are both XFNodes, whereas the site type differs between the two types.

Author:
hschneid

getTimeWindow

public float[] getTimeWindow(float time)
Returns the time window the node. For multiple time windows the last valid time window is searched and returned. If the given time is beyond the last valid time, the last time window is returned.
